https://wiki.qt.io/Qt_for_Beginners




1> install qt tools and library (after installing this you can directly build qt project and run)
sudo apt-get install qt4-dev-tools libqt4-dev libqt4-dev-bin qt4-qmake
2> write qt application.
3> build qt application
   qmake -project
   qmake
   make
   ./a.out
